-- AECI Forecasts Earnings Per Share for This Year Will Advance at Least 40%
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-10-14T08:32:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/aeci-forecasts-earnings-per-share-for-this-year-will-advance-at-least-40-.html
AECI Ltd. said full-year earnings
per share will be at least 40 percent higher than a year
earlier.  The company said its forecast could be adversely affected
should the rand strengthen further.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
